SECRET TIBETAN MENTALPHYSICS TEACHINGS - EDWIN DINGLE - PART 1

Extremely rare.

Part One of this collection is a one-hour documentary video on Mentalphysics, a course of Tibetan teachings on pranayama breathing exercises, meditation, and more. Mentalphysics was brought to the west in the early-mid twentienth century by Edwin John Dingle, an explorer who studied eastern esoteric teachings for several years in Singapore and Tibet. 

Be sure and search for the additional parts to this extremely rare collection of materials, and please do everything you can to help share them with others.
